Name
       timing_clock_uncertainty_from_to_precedence

Syntax
       timing_clock_uncertainty_from_to_precedence

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Sets the clock uncertainty precedence.

       When  set  to  true,  the software gives higher precedence to clock-to-
       clock uncertainty.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

